    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should reach out but what's the point? it's like trying to perform CPR on someone who's been dead for years. the version of me that was worth saving is just... gone. i'm just going through the motions of a life that isn't even mine anymore. i feel like i'm just taking up space for someone who isn't there.",
